  "prompt": "Which gift should I give to a girl on her birthday?",
  "response": "The best gift depends on several factors:\n\n1. Her interests and hobbies\n- If she likes reading, a book or e-reader\n- For music lovers, headphones or concert tickets\n- Sports enthusiasts might appreciate related gear\n\n2. Age considerations\n- Teenagers might like fashion accessories or tech gadgets\n- Young adults may prefer practical or experience-based gifts\n\n3. Budget\n- Personalized jewelry\n- Gift cards\n- Spa or beauty products\n- Handmade crafts\n- Experience gifts like concert/movie tickets\n- Skincare/makeup sets\n- Tech accessories\n- Hobby-related items\n\n4. Relationship context\n- Casual friend: Less personal, more generic gifts\n- Close friend/girlfriend: More thoughtful, personalized gifts\n\n5. Her personal preferences\n- Ask her friends/family\n- Pay attention to her hints\n- Consider her style and taste\n\nSome general safe options:\n- Portable charger\n- Cute/stylish bag\n- Scented candles\n- Chocolate/gourmet treats\n- Plants\n- Photo frame with memories\n\nThe most important thing is showing you've put thought into the gift.\n\nWould you like me to suggest something more specific based on her interests?",
